00:37:44.497 --> 00:37:50.399
I saw the people like a "Holy Ghost Woodstock"again outside.

00:37:50.400 --> 00:38:05.569
As I saw him standing, I saw a storm to the south and a storm to the east.

00:38:05.570 --> 00:38:14.480
I saw the light coming from the west. In the southeast, I saw all this storm.

00:38:14.481 --> 00:38:26.838
