00:38:26.839 --> 00:38:37.759
In the South, we have these dust devils that just turn up; it's not a tornado, but it's like a dust storm and it goes like a whirlwind.

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:55.919
But as this whirlwind was turning beside Pastor John in this vision, three doves came out of the sky and started circling in this whirlwind by him.

00:38:55.920 --> 00:39:09.272
