00:44:21.563 --> 00:44:28.159
But He said, 'Raise up prayer groups.'This will be birthed out of prayer.

00:44:28.160 --> 00:44:34.258
We must bring back prayer to the church. We must have great prayer groups at church, not flakiness.

00:44:34.259 --> 00:44:40.576
