00:45:24.240 --> 00:45:30.020
I don't want to hear about somebody else's business either. Do you understand what I'm saying?

00:45:30.021 --> 00:45:35.439
That's what the Lord is putting in my heart to tell y'all: we need prayer groups.

00:45:35.440 --> 00:45:44.233
All these major revivals were birthed out of prayer, and we've got to fill this with prayer for what's about to happen.

00:45:44.234 --> 00:45:50.078
And I saw Branson having a major revival. I want to be a part of wherever it's going to be.

00:45:50.079 --> 00:45:53.337
I know it's going to be in Collinsville. I know it's going to be in there.

00:45:53.338 --> 00:45:58.827
So you want to have two places so you can experience it both times.

