I just want my feet in the river. Whatever it takes. I want to be a part of prayer.

00:46:06.185 --> 00:46:11.767
I want to be a part of this great outpouring of the Spirit of God like we've never seen before.

00:46:11.768 --> 00:46:22.239
Do you understand? And I know that it's going to take some effort to get there. We've got to wake up.

00:46:22.240 --> 00:46:26.699
He's taking the lid off the septic and he's sucking it out and cleaning things up.

00:46:26.700 --> 00:46:33.194
Do you all understand? I hope you all understand the urgency of the hour.

00:46:33.195 --> 00:46:52.342
It's time to wake up in 2026. You're going to wake up. Then I was taken to Asia and I saw a massive ball glowing in Japan.

00:46:52.343 --> 00:47:19.472
I saw it highlighted with—it looked to me like platinum, the way platinum looks, like if you were to see transparent platinum where it's not solid-looking but it has a transparency to it like the streets of gold in heaven, but it was platinum.

00:47:19.473 --> 00:47:33.039
It was outlining Japan. And as it was outlined, it split down the middle with a major earthquake. It had a dome of a ball, a sphere that was cut in half.

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:52.556
And as it was glowing, it had some kind of—that platinum had light shining from the inside out that was so piercing that it looked like something out of some kind—it was half of a sun, but it was a platinum color.

00:47:52.557 --> 00:48:02.224
It wasn't yellow like the sun; it was like a platinum color like fire. It was like a light and it was shining out of Japan.

00:48:02.225 --> 00:48:20.799
But as I was looking and I gazed upon North Korea, I saw the people praying in their homes and they were singing but they had no words. They were not allowed to sing out loud in fear of their life.

00:48:20.800 --> 00:48:37.252
