00:49:02.160 --> 00:49:14.405
It made me want to weep because I saw all over and they had their hands and they were moving their fingers like this and they were doing it and they were smiling as big as they could.

00:49:14.406 --> 00:49:24.959
Their faces were glowing with joy worshipping our Father with no noise.

00:49:24.960 --> 00:49:40.719
I saw God take the Chinese flag. I saw the old communistic with the stars and the old flag. It's the China flag.

00:49:40.720 --> 00:49:48.851
I saw Him take their flag and He wadded it up in a ball with His fist and it was all crinkled up.

00:49:48.852 --> 00:49:54.242
That flag right there, He crinkled it up and He wadded it up like a ball.

00:49:54.243 --> 00:50:02.003
His fist was like this, but His hand was full of the flag. But I could see the stars and the red crinkling out of His hand.

00:50:02.004 --> 00:50:11.598
So I could see He was wrinkling it up like He was angry at it. All of a sudden, it was attached to North Korea.

00:50:11.599 --> 00:50:17.759
