00:50:32.176 --> 00:50:38.879
I saw highways that looked like tunnels and tubes all throughout the atmosphere.

00:50:38.880 --> 00:50:54.318
Now, I don't know how to describe these tubes to you, but they were round cylinder tubes that went from one place to another, and they were all like a superhighway above our atmosphere.

00:50:54.319 --> 00:51:00.152
There were lights of all kinds of colors coming through these tubes.

00:51:00.153 --> 00:51:14.015
It was almost like when you go to a bank and you send it out in the drive-thru and you put that in there and you push the button and the tube gets—the little thing gets—you put your money in and that gives it to the teller inside that tube.

00:51:14.016 --> 00:51:26.879
It was like tubes that went from America to Asia to other parts of South America, and there was a superhighway above us in the heavenlies.

00:51:26.880 --> 00:51:36.159
I don't know what I was seeing. There were purples and pinks, blues—all that was streaking like light through those.

00:51:36.160 --> 00:51:44.182
And there was no darkness in it. The tubes were lit up with light, all of them.

00:51:44.183 --> 00:51:54.879
But they were the size of what a human body would be. And it looked like spaghetti noodles all over the place.

00:51:54.880 --> 00:52:02.191
A superhighway all over the place. And it was like you would take one of those pickup sticks.

00:52:02.192 --> 00:52:06.441
That's how you know when you put the pickup sticks and you put it out and you pull it out.

00:52:06.442 --> 00:52:11.106
You don't want to get it to fall. The pickup sticks. Does anybody know what I'm talking about?

00:52:11.107 --> 00:52:20.504
The pickup sticks, the game, like the Erector—all kinds of different sticks and you pull the thing out and you pull it and they're all above the atmosphere.

00:52:20.505 --> 00:52:24.713
That's how many there were. It wasn't just a couple; it was thousands of them.

00:52:24.714 --> 00:52:34.635
And as they were all above the atmosphere, I saw people traveling in them like the money things that go in the bank.

00:52:34.636 --> 00:52:43.446
They were shooting through those tubes. And the Lord said, "Brandon, I will translate you there. I will translate my body in the days ahead.

00:52:43.447 --> 00:53:08.185
You'll be in one place in one minute talking on a camera like this, talking on YouTube, and I will translate you with whoever to go to that place where they're not allowed to have Christianity: Iran, places of the Middle East, and I will bring the gospel to them.

00:53:08.186 --> 00:53:24.109
If they won't allow you in, I will let you in."I saw tubes of people traveling all over in this end-time revival where you think that you won't be able to get in, but He said, "I'll take you in there.

00:53:24.110 --> 00:53:42.692
They may not let you in, but I will."I saw people going like Star Trek and they were laying hands on people and they were getting baptized in the Holy Ghost, and the glory of the Lord was showing up in those houses and they were being radically healed and delivered by the power of God.

00:53:42.693 --> 00:54:01.439
As you finished, He would take you back home. He said, "I'll let you even film it on your phone to validate that you were there as a sign and a wonder in these last days.

00:54:01.440 --> 00:54:04.734
I'll let you validate the area."You know what I'm talking about?

00:54:04.735 --> 00:54:11.999
Like you not exposing the people in there so they lose their life; God's not stupid.

00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:19.409
But it was like a witness somehow. I don't know how, like you're there and you're traveling around.

00:54:19.410 --> 00:54:30.594
Maybe you won't go into someone's house in North Korea and film them and say, "I want to video you and have ministry."I'm not trying to be flaky with this; this is how the Lord showed me, folks.

00:54:30.595 --> 00:54:34.944
You know what I'm saying? And it was translating all over the place.

00:54:34.945 --> 00:54:39.691
It was not just one place; it was all in South America. I saw it translating.

00:54:39.692 --> 00:54:51.999
I saw—am I using the word right?—translate, to go all over the place, and the glory of the Lord showed up.

00:54:52.000 --> 00:55:01.519
Healings, demonstrations, and manifestations like you wouldn't believe; I'm telling you, souls are coming to the kingdom of God.

00:55:01.520 --> 00:55:13.835
He said, "You're asking me to come, but there's millions of people in North Korea that have never heard the gospel."A highway—it's what He called it—a supernatural highway.

00:55:13.836 --> 00:55:25.512
And I'm going to take you into Asia and you'll be preaching, and you'll be in a prayer group and all of a sudden you'll be in North Korea, you'll be in Vietnam, and I'll have you there.

00:55:25.513 --> 00:55:34.916
And He said you'll hear their language and you'll speak their language and know exactly what they're saying through supernatural interpretation.

00:55:34.918 --> 00:55:41.707
You're saying transport. Transport through language, no language barriers.

00:55:41.708 --> 00:55:49.919
You'll know North Korea, you'll know whatever, and you'll be able to just talk to them and they'll be able to talk to you.

00:55:49.920 --> 00:55:59.999
There will be a supernatural on your mind. I saw working with the angelic host. The Lord said, "You will work with the angels.

00:56:00.000 --> 00:56:20.959
You'll work with the angels in the days ahead as a sign."He said, "I don't want any should perish, Brandon, but when this gospel is preached as a witness into all the earth, then will the end come."North Korea cannot be left out.

00:56:20.960 --> 00:56:28.787
Iran's people can't be left out. He's coming; He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:56:28.788 --> 00:56:40.798
And He showed me even into the islands that have not been really witnessed to, He was going to show up. I saw the glory of the Lord.

00:56:40.799 --> 00:56:50.120
As I saw all this and I saw what He was about to do with the North Koreans and all this stuff, I got so excited after I got finished with this video.

00:56:50.121 --> 00:56:54.372
I haven't been able to stop thinking about it. I know what the Lord showed me.

00:56:54.373 --> 00:57:00.153
I know what He said: that it's about the souls. He died for them.

00:57:00.154 --> 00:57:08.625
And I'll continue to tell you about the holes in His hands and the holes in His feet.

00:57:08.626 --> 00:57:17.229
As He walked, He showed me the harvest, similar to what John Kilpatrick was standing by; the harvest was plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:57:17.230 --> 00:57:32.033
He said, "It's all hands on deck. This is an all-hands-on-deck moment."I'm looking for the person who will just say, "Yes, here am I, Lord.

00:57:32.034 --> 00:57:47.070
Send me."I'll go to Walmart today. I'll talk to the little widow lady who doesn't have anyone to talk to on the park bench. I'll go to the playground and talk to the single mothers.

