00:58:41.418 --> 00:58:46.318
I'm telling you, we're about to see things like you wouldn't believe, y'all.

00:58:46.319 --> 00:58:53.354
But He wants you to have a prayer group. We're going to keep growing this channel, believing all to the glory of God.

00:58:53.355 --> 00:58:57.151
We'll hit over a million. I don't know; we'll see on this side or the other.

00:58:57.152 --> 00:59:04.187
I'm talking about South Korea. I know what He said, but I'm saying if it happens all in 2026, praise God.

00:59:04.188 --> 00:59:14.727
