00:59:14.728 --> 00:59:27.919
But if it doesn't, you just keep hitting it. It's the little drop in the cave that makes the indention.

00:59:27.920 --> 00:59:38.794
It's the little drop over a course of time. Don't get disappointed when the little drop doesn't show up and make an indention.

00:59:38.795 --> 00:59:53.714
It takes time. One drop at a time makes the mark. You walk in a cave and say, "How did that happen overnight?"No, that happened over time—quite some time.

00:59:53.715 --> 01:00:12.558
Some people say that's over thousands of years. And I'm like, "Wow, isn't that amazing?"Those stalactites and stalagmites that happened over thousands of years; it's inconsistency.

01:00:12.559 --> 01:00:15.802
It's being consistent with whatever God's called you to do.

01:00:15.803 --> 01:00:19.748
Don't get weary in well-doing, church. Keep your head up high.

01:00:19.749 --> 01:00:24.704
Yeah, we see the storms and all the stuff going on around us, but we need to be the salt.

01:00:24.705 --> 01:00:28.584
