You go, "I don't know what you're on, but you're not in reality over here."As much as I want to be excited about what you're saying, we live in the real world.

01:01:04.337 --> 01:01:16.639
You live on the hill. It's interesting to me, you know, where some people want to try to hype things up, but we'll just keep fighting.

01:01:16.640 --> 01:01:21.633
We fight the good fight of faith. Now, we're going to pray for New Year's Eve.

