01:01:43.455 --> 01:01:47.433
I still believe with all my heart the Lord showed me certain cryptos.

01:01:47.434 --> 01:01:54.719
Yeah, it took a nosedive this week, didn't it? I was like, "Oh no, it's going to zero.

01:01:54.720 --> 01:02:08.479
Oh no, it's going to zero."That's what it felt like. Oh no. But Braden goes, "Dad, I don't want to look at it."I said, "Neither do I.

01:02:08.480 --> 01:02:12.872
Neither do I."You know, but we know what the Lord has shown us in the future.

01:02:12.873 --> 01:02:19.199
I believe with all my heart that something's going to come out of this.

01:02:19.200 --> 01:02:22.526
