As we hear what His heart is for the North Koreans, the Asians, the South Americans, and all of the Middle East, He wants that no man should perish but all come to repentance.

01:17:36.640 --> 01:17:41.599
But unless a man is born again, he cannot enter the kingdom of God.

01:17:41.600 --> 01:17:54.799
Tonight's the night for you to turn before a holy God and say, 'Jesus, I need a Savior.'He's knocking on the door of your heart right now.

