You can see your life and how much of a shambles it is without the Lord.

01:18:26.007 --> 01:18:32.460
Now the Lord is standing at the door of your heart. Just like I told you, He came up with this in the visions of the past.

01:18:32.461 --> 01:18:44.079
He's knocking on the door. Not everybody will open the door for Jesus, but He's always there—an ever-present help in a time of need.

01:18:44.080 --> 01:18:55.039
He has the whole package for you this beautiful Christmas season. He's standing at the door of your heart.

