01:19:29.224 --> 01:19:35.039
I want you to put in the comment section right now, 'I need to be saved.

01:19:35.040 --> 01:19:39.279
I want to turn from my wicked ways.'Brandon, I want to turn from all this.

01:19:39.280 --> 01:19:44.879
I don't want to be a part of... I'm having a hard time through these holidays. I don't want to do this anymore.

01:19:44.880 --> 01:19:49.597
I feel like I'm at the end of my rope, but tonight Jesus just threw you a lifeline.

01:19:49.598 --> 01:20:00.158
