01:20:32.354 --> 01:20:40.334
I turn my back on the devil. I turn my back on my past. And from this day forward, Lord, I serve You with all my heart.

01:20:40.335 --> 01:20:46.758
I may mess up, Lord, but I'll pick myself up and I'll follow You even again and again and again.

01:20:46.759 --> 01:20:56.639
